curb-your-enthusiasm-richard-lewis-disliked-larry-david-first-met-1235705296%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fcurb-your-enthusiasm-richard-lewis-disliked-larry-david-first-met-1235705296%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gunman%20Kills%203%20In%20US'%20Florida%2C%20Cops%20Flag%20%26quot%3BDisgusting%20Ideology%20Of%20Hate%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20white%20man%20driven%20by%20racial%20hatred%20shot%20dead%20three%20Black%20people%20in%20a%20Florida%20discount%20store%20Saturday%20before%20taking%20his%20own%20life%20after%20a%20standoff%20with%20police%2C%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20targeted%20a%20certain%20group%20of%20people%20and%20that's%20Black%20people.%20That's%20what%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20kill.%20And%20that's%20very%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacksonville%20Sheriff%20TK%20Waters%20told%20a%20news%20conference%20about%20the%20gunman%2C%20who%20was%20in%20his%20early%2020s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sheriff's%20office%2C%20the%20shooter%2C%20who%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20identified%2C%20entered%20a%20Dollar%20General%20store%20wearing%20a%20tactical%20vest%2C%20armed%20with%20an%20AR-style%20rifle%20and%20a%20handgun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManifestos%20discovered%20by%20the%20gunman's%20family%20shortly%20before%20the%20attack%20%26quot%3Bdetail%20the%20shooter's%20disgusting%20ideology%20of%20hate%2C%26quot%3B%20Waters%20said%2C%20and%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20guns%20had%20hand-drawn%20swastikas%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20took%20place%20near%20Edward%20Waters%20University%2C%20a%20historically%20Black%20college%20in%20the%20southern%20US%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20shooter%20had%20been%20on%20campus%20earlier%20that%20day%2C%20though%20no%20one%20was%20harmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20on-campus%20Edward%20Waters%20University%20security%20officer%20engaged%20an%20unidentified%20male%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20Centennial%20Library%20on%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20individual%20refused%20to%20identify%20themselves%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added%2C%20adding%20the%20individual%20--%20later%20identified%20as%20the%20shooter%20--%20left%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20will%20investigate%20the%20shooting%20as%20a%20hate%20crime%2C%20said%20Sherri%20Onks%2C%20the%20bureau's%20special%20agent%20for%20Jacksonville%2C%20a%20city%20of%20nearly%20one%20million%20in%20the%20northeast%20corner%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20evidence%20the%20shooter%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20group%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20he%20acted%20completely%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Waters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Horrific'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMass%20shootings%20have%20become%20disturbingly%20common%20across%20the%20United%20States%2C%20with%20easy%20access%20to%20firearms%20in%20most%20states%20and%20more%20guns%20in%20the%20country%20than%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlorida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20decried%20the%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%26quot%3B%20shooting%20and%20called%20the%20gunman%20a%20%26quot%3Bscumbag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20targeting%20people%20based%20on%20their%20race%2C%20that%20is%20totally%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DeSantis%2C%20who%20is%20vying%20to%20be%20the%20Republican%20Party's%20presidential%20candidate%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20guy%20killed%20himself%20rather%20than%20face%20the%20music%20and%20accept%20responsibility%20for%20his%20actions%20and%20so%20he%20took%20the%20coward's%20way%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20was%20part%20of%20a%20weekend%20spate%20of%20gun%20violence%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3