5Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20hours%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20that%20the%20touchdown%20spot%20of%20the%20Vikram%20lander%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20would%20from%20now%20onwards%20be%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Shiv%20Shakti'%20point.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20August%2023%2C%20when%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20became%20successful%2C%20will%20be%20now%20known%20as%20National%20Space%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visibly%20emotional%20PM%20Modi%20addressed%20scientists%20at%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20organisation's%20command%20centre%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20and%20lauded%20them%20for%20their%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20August%2023rd%2C%20India%20hoisted%20the%20flag%20on%20the%20Moon.%20From%20now%20onwards%2C%20that%20day%20will%20be%20known%20as%20National%20Space%20Day%20in%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20PM%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20am%20very%20feeling%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20happiness%20among%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20beaming%20PM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20kind%20of%20happiness...%20these%20are%20very%20rare%20occasions%20when%20the%20whole%20body%20and%20soul%20is%20drenched%20in%20happiness%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20scientists%20at%20ISRO's%20Telemetry%20Tracking%20and%20Command%20Network%20Mission%20Control%20Complex%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20scientists%20had%20taken%20the%20Make%20In%20India%20initiative%20to%20the%20Moon%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20boost%20to%20indigenous%20productions%20due%20to%20Chandrayaan%203's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20he%20was%20on%20a%20two-nation%20visit%20to%20South%20Africa%20and%20Greece%20but%20his%20mind%20was%20completely%20with%20the%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20wanted%20to