should%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20owner%2Fmanager%20of%20the%20hotel.%20In%20the%20past%20as%20well%2C%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20with%20minors%20have%20occurred%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20are%20investigating%20as%20to%20what%20guidelines%20have%20been%20issued%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20regarding%20booking%2Fstay%20by%20minors%20in%20hotels%20and%20for%20ensuring%20their%20safety.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20these%20cases%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%20at%20Jagatpuri%20police%20station.%20In%20the%20past%20as%20well%2C%20several%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20wherein%20many%20minor%20girls%20were%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20accused%20persons%20in%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20DCW%20Chairperson%20Swati%20Maliwal%20has%20issued%20notice%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20seeking%20action%20taken%20report%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20has%20sought%20the%20details%20of%20action%20taken%20against%20the%20hotel.%20It%20also%20asked%20whether%20the%20manager%2Fowner%20of%20the%20hotel%20had%20been%20arrested%20or%20not%20and%20sought%20the%20details%20of%20the%20association%20of%20any%20aggregator%20with%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCW%20has%20also%20sought%20details%20of%20FIRs%20wherein%20women%20and%20minor%20girls%20have%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20hotels%20and%20the%20present%20status%20of%20the%20cases%20and%20has%20asked%20for%20action%20taken%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20hotels%2C%20where%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20with%20minors%20have%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20Commission%20has%20sought%20the%20details%20of%20any%20rules%2Fguidelines%20issued%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20with%20respect%20to%20booking%2Fstaying%20by%20minors%20in%20hotels.%20It%20has%20also%20sought%20details%20of%20steps%20taken%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20and%20minor%20girls%20in%20hotels%2Fguest%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693067640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F4gtlrbrs_swati-maliwal-1200_625x300_11_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsex-assault-of-2-minors-in-hotel-cant-be-coincidence-womens-body-head-swati-maliwal-4331791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20on%20Saturday%20issued%20notice%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20over%20two%20separate%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20assault%20involving%20two%20minor%20girls%20in%20the%20same%20hotel%20in%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsex-assault-of-2-minors-in-hotel-cant-be-coincidence-womens-body-head-swati-maliwal-4331791%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsex-assault-of-2-minors-in-hotel-cant-be-coincidence-womens-body-head-swati-maliwal-4331791%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsex-assault-of-2-minors-in-hotel-cant-be-coincidence-womens-body-head-swati-maliwal-4331791%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Khushi%20Kapoor's%20chic%20sartorial%20choices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693067400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103067566%2Cimgsize-52258.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fkhushi-kapoors-chic-sartorial-choices%2Fphotostory%2F103067566.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103067566.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BKhushi%20Kapoor's%20chic%20sa