vel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20world%20football's%20governing%20body%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20explaining%20it%20would%20last%2090%20days%2C%20pending%20their%20disciplinary%20proceedings.%20Rubiales%20kissed%20Hermoso%20after%20Spain's%20victory%20over%20England%20but%20Hermoso%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Spanish%20FA%20chief%20did%20not%20have%20her%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20attracted%20criticism%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20world%20with%20the%20footballers'%20union%20Futpro%20saying%20that%2081%20players%20were%20striking%20and%20will%20not%20play%20for%20the%20national%20side%20till%20Rubiales%20was%20removed.%20However%2C%20the%20Spanish%20FA%20chief%20remained%20defiant%20and%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20will%20not%20step%20down%20from%20his%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers%20from%20World%20Cup%20runners-up%20England%20released%20a%20statement%20in%20support%20of%20Hermoso%20on%20their%20social%20networks%2C%20signed%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lionesses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnacceptable%20actions%20allowed%20to%20happen%20by%20a%20sexist%20and%20patriarchal%20organisation.%20Abuse%20is%20abuse%20and%20we%20have%20all%20seen%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20behaviour%20of%20those%20who%20think%20they%20are%20invincible%20must%20not%20be%20tolerated%20and%20people%20shouldn't%20need%20convincing%20to%20take%20action%20against%20any%20form%20of%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20stand%20with%20you%2C%20Jenni%20Hermoso%2C%20and%20all%20players%20of%20the%20Spanish%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20tournament%2015%20Spain%20players%20had%20taken%20a%20similar%20strike%20against%20the%20federation%20and%20coach%20Jorge%20Vilda%2C%20but%20many%20relented%20and%20three%20were%20part%20of%20the%20team's%20triumph%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20players%2C%20including%20double%20Ballon%20d'Or%20winner%20Alexia%20Putellas%2C%20published%20messages%20of%20support%20for%20Hermoso%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Friday%2C%20some%20including%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bit's%20over%26quot%3B%20--%20potentially%20referring%20to%20Rubiales'%20leadership%20of%20Spanish%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20Putellas%2C%20Hermoso%2C%20player%20of%20the%20tournament%20Aitana%20Bonmati%20and%20many%20more%20say%20they%20will%20not%20play%20for%20Spain%20again%20until%20Rubiales%20and%20potentially%20others%20leave%20their%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federation%20also%20appeared%20to%20send%20a%20thinly%20veiled%20threat%20to%20the%20striking%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RFEF%20respects%2C%20as%20it%20has%20always%20respected%2C%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20players%20who%20wish%20to%20participate%20or%20not%20with%20the%20Spanish%20national%20team%20in%20international%20matches%2C%20although%20it%20is%20clear%20national%20team%20duty%20is%20an%20obligation%20for%20all%20federated%20persons%20if%20they%20are%20called%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RFEF%20added%20in%20their%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spanish%20government%20have%20started%20a%20process%20which%20may%20allow%20them%20to%20suspend%20Rubiales%20from%20his%20post%20next%20week%2C%20while%20FIFA%20have%20opened%20a%20disciplinary%20investigation%20into%20his%20behaviour%20at%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20AFP%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693053480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fmj0ojk2_asfaf_625x300_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Ffifa-suspends-spanish-fa-chief-following-kiss-row-in-womens-world-cup-final-4332081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22FIFA%20suspended%20Luis%20Rubiales%20as%20president%20of%20Spain's%20football%20federation%20for%20kissing%20Spanish%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20player%20Jenni%20Hermoso%20on%20the%20lips.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Ffifa-suspends-spanish-fa-chief-following-kiss-row-in-womens-world-cup-final-4332081%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Ffifa-suspends-spanish-fa-chief-following-kiss-row-in-womens-world-cup-final-4332081%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Ffifa-suspends-spanish-fa-chief-following-kiss-row-in-womens-world-cup-final-4332081%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Real%20Culprit%20Behind%20the%20Death%20of%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20Student%20is%20Patriarchy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26112642%2FIMG_1122.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20many%20know%20by%20now%2C%20on%20August%209%2C%20a%2017-year-old%20first%20semester%20undergraduate%20student%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-swapnadeep-kundu%5C%22%3Efell%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20Jadavpur%20University%20Main%20Hostel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20had%20just%20become%20a%20boarder.%20He%20died%20at%20a%20hospital%20the%20next%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20quick%20to%20identify%20patriarchy%20as%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20any%20kind%20of%20violence%20only%20when%20the%20act%20is%20perpetrated%20on%20women%20by%20men.%20What%20this%20analysis%20does%20is%20occlude%20the%20way%20not%20just%20inter-gender%2C%20but%20also%20intra-gender%20violence%20is%20an%20enactment%20of%20patriarchy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20early%20as%201969%2C%20Kate%20Millett%20had%20said%20that%20a%20patriarchal%20society%20is%20a%20society%20%E2%80%98organised%20along%20the%20principles%20of%20men%20dominating%20women%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eolder%20men%20dominating%20younger%20men%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20the%20family%20being%20the%20unit%20of%20the%20patriarchal%20whole%E2%80%99.%20The%20emphasis%20is%20mine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20now%20been%20established%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%20that%20the%20undergraduate%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20ragging%20perpetrated%20on%20him%20by%20boarders%20who%20were%20all%20older%20than%20him.%20These%20boarders%20were%20not%20all%20senior%20students.%20A%20few%20had%20long%20ceased%20to%20be%20students%20of%20the%20university%2C%20but%20had%20stayed%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20understand%20how%20patriarchy%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20malaise%20called%20ragging%2C%20one%20has%20to%20understand%20how%20patriarchy%20works.%20It%20is%20a%20violent%20structure%20that%20constantly%20renews%20its%20acceptability%20in%20society%20by%20presenting%20itself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98loving%20and%20caring%E2%80%99%20one.%20Thus%2C%20%E2%80%98loving%20and%20caring%E2%80%99%20parents%20force%20their%20children%20to%20study%20subjects%20that%20are%20not%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20liking%2C%20to%20take%20up%20jobs%20that%20leave%20the%20children%20unhappy%2C%20and%20to%20marry%20a%20person%20that%20makes%20their%20marital%20life%20one%20of%20anguish.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%98loving%20and%20caring%E2%80%99%20patriarchy%20that%20seeks%20to%20%E2%80%98protect%E2%80%99%20women%20by%20restricting%20their%20movements%2C%20dictating%20their%20clothing%2C%20even%20prescribing%20the%20amount%20of%20food%20that%20is%20suitable%20for%20women%20(less%20than%20the%20amount%20allowed%20for%20their%20brothers%20and%20husbands%2C%20of%20course).%20Ragging%20is%20one%20such%20%E2%80%98loving%20and%20caring%E2%80%99%20activity%20that%20hostel%20seniors%20enjoy%20subjecting%20their%20juniors%20to%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98building%20their%20character%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20ostensibly%20toughening%20them%20up%20for%20the%20big%2C%20bad%20world%20outside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20bizarrely%2C%20ragging%20is%20justified%20by%20the%20claim%20that%20it%20helps%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20friendship%20amongst%20the%20boarders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22school%20education%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20one%20of%20my%20morning%20classes%2C%20I%20was%20not%20a%20little%20annoyed%20to%20see%20a%20student%20struggling%20to%20keep%20his%20eyes%20open%20even%20though%20he%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20first%20bench.%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20jump%20to%20the%20usual%20conclusion%20that%20he%20was%20insulting%20me%20by%20implying%20that%20my%20class%20was%20boring.%20I%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20was%20so%20sleepy.%20He%20confessed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20sleep%20the%20previous%20night.%20I%20asked%20him%20why.%20He%20simply%20said%20that%20he%20was%20a%20hostel%20boarder.%20I%20understood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20immediate%20thought%20was%20to%20get%20him%20out%20of%20the%20hostel%2C%20but%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20he%20was%20not%20the%20only%20student%20of%20his%20batch%20who%20had%20been%20kept%20awake%20all%20night%2C%20and%20that%20removing%20one%20student%20from%20the%20hostel%20would%20not%20solve%20the%20problem.%20I%20kept%20checking%20on%20him.%20Eventually%20he%20said%20that%20the%20ragging%20had%20stopped%20because%20now%20there%20were%20newer%20boarders.%20I%20was%20numbed%20at%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20he%20said%20those%20words.%20Like%20numerous%20other%20patriarchal%20systems%20at%20work%20in%20society%2C%20ragging%20continues%20because%20of%20a%20general%20agreement%20that%20%E2%80%98it%20is%20good%20for%20you.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20R.W.%20Connell%20theorised%20%E2%80%98hegemonic%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20what%20evolved%20into%20Masculinity%20Studies%20%E2%80%93%20she%20also%20theorised%20%E2%80%98complicit%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98subordinate%20masculinity%E2%80%99.%20All%20three%20kinds%20of%20masculinity%20are%20in%20constant%20evidence%20at%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostels.%20%E2%80%98Hegemonic%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20belongs%20to%20the%20seniors%2C%20%E2%80%98complicit%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20belongs%20to%20all%20the%20men%20associated%20with%20the%20hostel%20who%20allow%20the%20seniors%20unfettered%20freedom%20to%20nakedly%20exhibit%20their%20%E2%80%98power%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98subordinate%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20belongs%20to%20the%20freshers.%20The%20brutal%20irony%20is%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98subordinate%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20can%2C%20and%20often%20does%2C%20become%20tomorrow%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98complicit%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98hegemonic%20masculinity%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20men%20create%20a%20micro-patriarchal%20society%20in%20the%20hostel%20and%20effectively%20become%20a%20law%20unto%20themselves%3B%20so%20much%20so%20that%20even%20the%20police%20is%20not%20allowed%20entry%20into%20the%20hostel%20unless%20the%20university%20authority%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20concerned%20hostel%20allows%20such%20an%20intervention.%20A%20sense%20of%20impunity%20encases%20these%20boarders%20and%20it%20empowers%20them%20even%20to%20make%20lewd%20remarks%20at%20inhabitants%20of%20other%20residential%20buildings%20in%20the%20locality.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20these%20lewd%20remarks%20are%20essentially%20patriarchal%20in%20nature%3A%20objectifying%20the%20women%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20and%20shouting%20salacious%20suggestions%20at%20them%20are%20all%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%98harmless%2C%20high-spirited%20fun%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-media-trial%5C%22%3EA%20Shrill%20Media%20Trial%20Against%20Jadavpur%20University%E2%80%99s%20Students%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Drown%20Out%20the%20Real%20Issue%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20we%20forget%20is%20that%20these%20men%20eventually%20get%20married%20and%20bring%20to%20the%20marriage%20all%20of%20the%20misogyny%20that%20they%20have%20trained%20themselves%20in%20over%20all%20their%20school%2C%20college%2C%20and%20university%20years.%20It%20is%20these%20men%20who%2C%20%E2%80%98trapped%E2%80%99%20in%20unhappy%20marriages%2C%20flood%20social%20media%20with%20memes%20that%20make%20fun%20of%20married%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20%E2%80%98love%E2%80%99%20for%20their%20girlfriends%20and%20later%20wives%20are%20of%20a%20piece%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98loving%20and%20caring%E2%80%99%20patriarchy%20that%20I%20spoke%20about%20earlier.%20They%20learn%20to%20identify%20the%20feminine%20as%20the%20real%20enemy.%20They%20demand%20%E2%80%98true%20femininity%E2%80%99%20from%20their%20girlfriends%20and%20wives%3A%20silence.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20only%20to%20be%20expected%20that%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostels%20are%20marked%20by%20loud%20and%20proud%20declarations%20of%20homophobia%20(because%20gay%20men%20are%20regarded%20by%20these%20men%20as%20being%20%E2%80%98not%20quite%20men%E2%80%99)%20and%20transphobia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20one%20of%20the%20last%20words%20heard%20from%20the%20student%20who%20died%20was%20a%20declaration%20that%20he%20is%20not%20gay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%20therefore%20that%20he%20was%20subjected%20to%20ragging%20that%20was%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20homophobic%2C%20and%20it%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20homophobia%20and%20transphobia%20are%20as%20patriarchal%20as%20misogyny%20or%20indeed%2C%20misandry.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20male%20homosexuality%20so%20threatening%20to%20these%20%E2%80%93%20presumably%20100%25%20heterosexual%20%E2%80%93%20men%3F%20It%20is%20simply%20because%20they%20fear%20that%20the%20male%20homosexual%20would%20objectify%20them%20exactly%20the%20way%20they%20themselves%20objectify%20women.%20They%20are%20happy%20to%20demean%20but%20will%20not%20be%20demeaned%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETied%20to%20the%20notion%20of%20objectification%20is%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20body%3B%20the%20body%20as%20the%20object%2C%20the%20body%20as%20a%20presence%20that%20is%20not%20human%20unless%20society%20declares%20it%20to%20be%20so.%20What%20is%20deeply%20patriarchal%20about%20Ren%C3%A9%20Descartes%E2%80%99%20notorious%20declaration%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ecogito%20ergo%20sum%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(I%20think%2C%20therefore%20I%20am)%20is%20that%20it%20is%20thought%20that%20gives%20the%20body%20any%20identity.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20mind%20is%20assigned%20a%20superior%20position%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20body.%20In%20various%20cultures%20across%20the%20world%2C%20women%20are%20denied%20opportunities%20to%20fully%20develop%20their%20minds%20lest%20they%20cease%20to%20be%20purely%20just%20bodies.%20So%2C%20in%20patriarchal%20culture%2C%20mind%20becomes%20gendered%20male%2C%20and%20body%2C%20female.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20%E2%80%98feminise%E2%80%99%20and%20therefore%20disempower%20a%20man%20is%20to%20strip%20him%20naked%2C%20against%20his%20will.%20We%20have%20repeatedly%20seen%20visual%20examples%20of%20how%20groups%20of%20men%20have%20been%20stripped%20naked%20in%20order%20to%20dehumanise%20and%20therefore%20feminize%20them%3A%20be%20it%20the%20Jews%20at%20Nazi%20concentration%20camps%20or%20the%20prisoners%20at%20Abu%20Ghraib%20or%20indeed%20Dalit%20men%20in%20India.%20The%20student%20at%20Jadavpur%20University%20hostel%20was%20also%20stripped%20naked%2C%20thereby%20dehumanising%20and%20%E2%80%98feminising%E2%80%99%20him%20at%20one%20and%20the%20same%20time.%20So%2C%20the%20nudity%20thrust%20upon%20him%20was%20also%20a%20patriarchal%20act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-639193%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20believe%20that%20patriarchy%20is%20ultimately%20responsible%20for%20the%20horrific%20incident%2C%20what%20we%20have%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20very%20often%2C%20if%20not%20always%2C%20it%20is%20the%20parents%20who%20train%20their%20children%20in%20patriarchy%20with%20much%20%E2%80%98loving%20care%E2%80%99.%20How%20often%20have%20we%20heard%20a%20parent%20tell%20their%20son%20who%20has%20come%20home%20crying%20from%20school%20because%20he%20has%20been%20bullied%2C%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20cry%20like%20a%20girl!%20Fight%20like%20a%20boy!%E2%80%99%3F%20Boys%20are%20taught%2C%20often%20by%20their%20parents%2C%20that%20violence%20is%20the%20correct%20way%20to%20solve%20all%20problems.%20Gradually%20boys%20learn%20to%20be%20verbally%20violent%20%E2%80%93%20a%20common%20form%20of%20ragging%20is%20to%20ask%20a%20fresher%20how%20many%20swear%20words%20he%20knows%20%E2%80%93%20and%20then%20to%20be%20physically%20violent.%20Soon%20they%20are%20also%20encouraged%20to%20be%20violent%20to%20their%20own%20body%20%E2%80%93%20destroy%20the%20lungs%20by%20smoking%2C%20destroy%20the%20liver%20by%20drinking%2C%20destroy%20the%20skull%20by%20not%20wearing%20a%20helmet%20while%20riding%20a%20bike!%20%E2%80%93%20and%20thus%20consolidate%20the%20prized%20position%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98a%20real%20man%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Real%20men%20don%E2%80%99t%20rape!%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20%E2%80%98real%20men%E2%80%99%20give%20rape%20threats%2C%20I%20presume.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20across%20West%20Bengal%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20rush%20to%20install%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20all%20nooks%20and%20crannies%20of%20college%20and%20university%20hostels.%20This%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20treating%20the%20symptom%20and%20not%20the%20disease.%20CCTV%20cameras%20can%20record%20and%20monitor%20the%20comings%20and%20goings%20along%20hostel%20corridors%2C%20but%20how%20do%20we%20record%20and%20monitor%20the%20widespread%20encouragement%20of%20patriarchal%20behaviour%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20cases%20such%20as%20the%20one%20that%20has%20happened%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20do%20we%20stop%20the%20casual%20patriarchy%20that%20is%20spouted%20by%20college%20and%20university%20teachers%20inside%20the%20classroom%3F%20How%20do%20we%20stop%20the%20pervasive%20disparaging%20of%20the%20feminine%20in%20a%20society%20where%20the%20only%20normal%20and%20acceptable%20is%20the%20hegemonic%20masculine%3F%20Unless%20we%20are%20prepared%20to%20acknowledge%20these%20questions%20and%20take%20institutional%20steps%20to%20answer%20them%2C%20such%20incidents%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20place.%20We%20will%20express%20our%20deepest%20condolences%20and%20then%20return%20to%20our%20deepest%20patriarchal%20comfort%20zones%2C%20as%20if%20all%20is%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENiladri%20R.%20Chatterjee%20is%20professor%20at%20the%20department%20of%20English%2C%20University%20of%20Kalyani.%20His%20latest%20book%20is%20titled%20%3C%2Fem%3EEntering%20the%20Maze%3A%20Queer%20Fiction%20of%20Krishnagopal%20Mallick.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693053059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26112642%2FIMG_1122.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-patriarchy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unless%20we%20are%20prepared%20to%20acknowledge%20these%20questions%20and%20take%20institutional%20steps%20to%20answer%20them%2C%20such%20incidents%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-patriarchy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20drops%20teaser%20of%20new%20song%20from%20'Jawan'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693052614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103089462%2Cimgsize-20262.cms%22%2C%22originI