Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-katrina-kaif-jacqueline-fernandez-best-dressed-celebs-of-the-week%2Farticleshow%2F103085660.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103085660.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFrom%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20Malaika%20Arora%20to%20Sara%20Ali%20Khan%20-%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20best%20dress%20celebs%20of%20the%20week%20to%20get%20some%20fashion%20inspiration!%20Find%20out%20who%20wore%20what%20and%20slayed%20this%20week!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-katrina-kaif-jacqueline-fernandez-best-dressed-celebs-of-the-week%2Farticleshow%2F103085660.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Photos%20of%20doomed%20Franklin%20explorers%20to%20go%20to%20auction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693044300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-s-stanley-franklins-expedition_6263170.jpg%3F20230826125524%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fphotos-of-explorers-from-doomed-franklin-expedition-to-be-auctioned-12947818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20unique%20set%20of%20portraits%20from%20the%20doomed%201845%20Franklin%20expedition%20to%20Canada's%20Northwest%20Passage%20is%20to%20be%20auctioned%20for%20an%20estimated%20six-figure%20sum.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A107%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fphotos-of-explorers-from-doomed-franklin-expedition-to-be-auctioned-12947818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fphotos-of-explorers-from-doomed-franklin-expedition-to-be-auctioned-12947818%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fphotos-of-explorers-from-doomed-franklin-expedition-to-be-auctioned-12947818%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Constitution%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20Colonial%20Imposition%20%E2%80%93%20It%20Emerged%20From%20a%20Great%20Mass%20Movement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F15105244%2Fconstitution-of-india.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20energy%20has%20been%20expended%20on%20elaborating%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20more%20than%20often%20in%20legal%20terms.%20It%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20lawyer%E2%80%99s%20paradise.%20The%20argument%20in%20this%20essay%20suggests%20that%20the%20constitution%20can%20be%20predominantly%20thought%20of%20as%20a%20political%20document.%20As%20a%20political%20document%2C%20it%20is%20prescriptive%20as%20well%20as%20regulatory.%20The%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20prescriptive%20because%20it%20institutionalises%20the%20ideals%20of%20democracy.%20Left%20to%20itself%2C%20democracy%20can%20go%20completely%20haywire.%20It%20can%20be%20reduced%20to%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20has%20been%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%20Equally%2C%20it%20can%20descend%20to%20mob%20rule%20that%20Greek%20philosophers%20were%20so%20wary%20of.%20Without%20a%20constitution%2C%20we%20will%20never%20know%20that%20there%20is%20more%20to%20democracy%20than%20just%20elections.%20Without%20a%20constitution%20that%20establishes%20that%20human%20beings%20deserve%20to%20be%20treated%20in%20certain%20ways%2C%20with%20dignity%2C%20and%20not%20to%20be%20treated%20in%20other%20ways%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20subjected%20to%20custodial%20torture%20%E2%80%93%20democracy%20will%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20after%20a%20winning%20party%20takes%20over%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElections%20are%20essential%20for%20democracy%2C%20but%20they%20are%20but%20a%20moment%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20democratic%20country.%20The%20essence%20of%20democracy%20is%20the%20right%20of%20human%20beings%20to%20live%20lives%20they%20consider%20worthy.%20In%20order%20to%20live%20worthwhile%20lives%2C%20every%20citizen%20has%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20the%20necessary%20preconditions%20of%20a%20good%20life%20ranging%20from%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty%2C%20the%20right%20to%20political%20participation%2C%20and%20the%20right%20to%20dissent%2C%20to%20the%20right%20to%20health%2C%20income%2C%20education%2C%20food%20and%20shelter.%20Without%20sustenance%2C%20a%20human%20being%20can%20hardly%20be%20free.%20Without%20liberty%2C%20an%20individual%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20she%20is%20not%20hungry%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20not%20free.%20All%20human%20beings%20are%20owed%20the%20preconditions%20of%20a%20fulfilling%20life.%20Below%20this%2C%20we%20cannot%20fall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20constitution%20is%20regulatory%20because%20liberal%20philosophers%20have%20been%20wary%20of%20two%20factors%20that%20can%20cripple%20democratic%20life%3A%20demagogues%20and%20brute%20majorities.%20They%20aspire%20to%20contain%20both%20these%20factors.%20In%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20on%20November%2025%2C%201948%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20warned%20that%20we%20can%20only%20maintain%20democracy%20when%20we%20observe%20the%20warning%20that%20the%20liberal%20philosopher%20John%20Stuart%20Mill%20had%20issued%20to%20all%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20the%20maintenance%20of%20democracy.%20People%20should%20not%20%E2%80%9Clay%20their%20liberties%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20even%20a%20great%20man%2C%20or%20to%20trust%20him%20with%20powers%20which%20enable%20him%20to%20subvert%20their%20institutions.%20There%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20in%20being%20grateful%20to%20great%20men%20who%20have%20rendered%20life-long%20service%20to%20the%20country%20but%20there%20are%20limits%20to%20gratefulness%E2%80%9D.%20He%20quoted%20the%20Irish%20Patriot%20Daniel%20O%E2%80%99Connel%20who%20had%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20man%20can%20be%20grateful%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20his%20honour%E2%80%A6%20and%20no%20nation%20can%20be%20grateful%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20its%20liberty.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20caution%2C%20continued%20Ambedkar%2C%20is%20even%20more%20necessary%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20in%20India%2C%20Bhakti%20or%20what%20may%20be%20called%20the%20path%20of%20devotion%20or%20hero-worship%2C%20plays%20a%20part%20in%20its%20politics%20unequalled%20in%20magnitude%20by%20the%20part%20it%20plays%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20any%20other%20country%20in%20the%20world.%20Bhakti%20in%20religion%20may%20be%20a%20road%20to%20salvation%20of%20the%20soul.%20But%20in%20politics%2C%20Bhakti%20or%20hero-worship%20is%20a%20sure%20road%20to%20degradation%20and%20to%20eventual%20dictatorship.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20warning%20was%20prescient%2C%20for%20Indians%20have%20revealed%20a%20troublesome%20propensity%20to%20hero-worship%20leaders%20they%20see%20as%20strong%20and%20decisive.%20This%20happens%20despite%20the%20recognition%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjnu-violence-bjp-strongmen%5C%22%3Emuscular%20populists%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20appeal%20to%20people%20directly%20over%20the%20head%20of%20institutions%20and%20procedures%20subvert%20democracy.%20Whether%20it%20is%20lawmaking%2C%20policy%20formulation%2C%20or%20justice%2C%20democratic%20procedures%20demand%20patience%20and%20sobriety%2C%20constant%20awareness%20of%20what%20the%20impact%20of%20policies%20will%20be%2C%20and%20constant%20vigilance%20against%20those%20who%20wreck%20constitutional%20integrity%20and%20propriety%20in%20impatient%20pursuit%20of%20their%20own%20interests.%20That%20is%20why%20democratic%20countries%20provide%20for%20bicameral%20legislatures%20so%20that%20sufficient%20time%20elapses%20between%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20Bill%20and%20its%20final%20adoption%20as%20law.%20Democracy%20requires%20not%20only%20patience%20and%20care%20by%20lawmakers%2C%20it%20requires%20a%20Janus-faced%20civil%20society%20that%20looks%20towards%20the%20state%20as%20well%20as%20power%20equations%20within%20its%20own%20domain.%20The%20task%20of%20civil%20society%20is%20to%20bring%20to%20light%20acts%20of%20omission%20and%20commission%20by%20the%20government%20as%20well%20as%20oppression%20within%20its%20own%20domain.%20The%20constitution%20regulates%20democracy%20through%20the%20institutionalisation%20of%20procedures%20and%20limits%20on%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20might%20have%20failed%20us%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20but%20constitutional%20guarantees%20of%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20have%20provided%20enough%20political%20inspiration%20to%20social%20movements%20to%20agitate%20for%20the%20realisation%20of%20rights.%20Civil%20society%20groups%20have%20mobilised%20for%20civil%20liberties%20since%20the%201970s%2C%20for%20environment%20protection%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20and%20for%20social%20rights%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20fourteen%20years%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20movements%2C%20anti-caste%20movements%2C%20the%20movement%20against%20communalism%2C%20and%20movements%20for%20the%20right%20to%20sexual%20preferences%20have%20highlighted%20urgent%20issues%20in%20the%20life%20of%20our%20society.%20Many%20of%20these%20movements%20have%20been%20backed%20by%20a%20supportive%20Supreme%20Court.%20Today%2C%20civil%20society%20is%20threatened%2C%20and%20limits%20on%20power%20have%20been%20dispensed%20with.%20Will%20this%20new%20elite%2C%20of%20a%20presumably%20New%20India%2C%20even%20know%20how%20to%20write%20a%20democratic%20constitution%20which%20can%20be%20compared%20favourably%20to%20our%20present%20one%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F474494-bibek-debroy.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-181247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBibek%20Debroy%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20economic%20advisory%20council%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98new%20constitution%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFiles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20constitution%20as%20a%20political%20document%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constitution%20is%20significant%20for%20Indians%20for%20several%20reasons.%20For%20one%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Indian%20constitution%20was%20not%20imposed%20upon%20us%20by%20a%20colonial%20power.%20It%20was%20the%20product%20of%20a%20mass%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20the%20culmination%20of%20one%20the%20greatest%20mass%20movements%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20The%20movement%20brought%20together%20members%20of%20all%20religions%20and%20creeds%2C%20class%2C%20caste%2C%20and%20gender.%20Leaders%2C%20public%20intellectuals%2C%20and%20progressive%20writers%20and%20poets%20inspired%20thousands%20of%20people%20to%20come%20together%20and%20protest%20against%20colonial%20policies%2C%20demonstrate%20against%20unjust%20laws%2C%20readily%20go%20to%20prison%2C%20and%20sacrifice%20their%20lives%20if%20necessary%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20right%20of%20Indians%20to%20forge%20their%20own%20future.%20Leaders%20demanded%20not%20only%20that%20Indians%20write%20their%20own%20constitution%20but%20that%20they%20do%20so%20in%20a%20Constituent%20Assembly%20elected%20by%20universal%20adult%20suffrage.%20Indians%20joined%20hands%20and%20marched%20together%2C%20fired%20up%20by%20passionate%20speeches%20and%20even%20more%20inspiring%20protest%20poetry%20in%20Urdu%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20long%2C%20Urdu%20was%20the%20language%20of%20informed%20and%20cultivated%20minds%20%E2%80%93%20evocative%2C%20elegant%20and%20beautiful.%20Today%2C%20Urdu%20is%20regarded%20as%20the%20language%20of%20the%20enemy%2C%20and%20Urdu%20speakers%20are%20identified%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99.%20The%20cynical%20politics%20of%20majoritarianism%20and%20defenders%20of%20Brahmanical%20and%20Sanskritic%20Hindi%20forget%20that%20revolutionary%20poetry%2C%20which%20mobilised%20an%20entire%20generation%20of%20freedom%20fighters%2C%20was%20written%20by%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20poets.%20For%20instance%2C%20Brij%20Narain%20Chakbast%20(1882-1926)%20movingly%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYeh%20Khaak%20e%20Hind%20se%20paide%20hain%20josh%20ke%20aasar%3Cbr%3E%5CnHimalaya%20se%20uthe%20jaise%20abr-e-daryabaar%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20dust%20of%20Hindustan%20have%20arisen%20signs%20of%20energy%20and%20passion%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20way%20rivers%20gush%20from%20the%20Himalayas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20Bismil%20Azimbadi%20(1901-1978)%20wrote%20the%20marvellous%20poem%20in%201921%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSarfaroshi%20Ki%20tammana%20ab%20hamare%20dil%20mein%20hai%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cndekhna%20hai%20zor%20kitna%20baazu-e-katil%20mein%20hain%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20passionately%20desire%20to%20lay%20down%20our%20lives%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%20let%20us%20see%20how%20much%20courage%20is%20there%20in%20the%20arms%20of%20the%20executioner%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaulana%20Hasrat%20Mohani%20(1875-1951)%20coined%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98Inquilab%20Zindabad%E2%80%99.%20This%20became%20the%20rallying%20cry%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20the%20anthem%20of%20revolutionaries.%20He%20demanded%20Azaadi%20e%20Kaamil%20or%20complete%20independence%20in%201921%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRasm%20e%20jafa%20kaamyab%20dekhiye%20kab%20tak%20rahe%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHubb%20e%20watan%20mast%20e%20khwab%20kab%20tak%20rahe%3Cbr%3E%5CnDaulat%20e%20Hindustan%20qabzah%20aghyar%20mein%3Cbr%3E%5CnBe%20adad%20O%20behisab%20dekhie%20kab%20tak%20rahe%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20see%20how%20long%20we%20are%20oppressed%3Cbr%3E%5CnHow%20long%20freedom%20remains%20but%20a%20dream%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20how%20long%20the%20British%20plunder%20India%E2%80%99s%20riches%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Raj%20Guru%2C%20and%20Sukhdev%20marched%20to%20the%20gallows%2C%20they%20raised%20the%20slogan%20of%20Inquilab%20Zindabad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F27122954%2Fbhagat-singh1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22785%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F27122954%2Fbhagat-singh1.jpg%20587w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F27122954%2Fbhagat-singh1-300x203.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-228050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBhagat%20Singh%2C%20Sukhdev%20and%20Rajguru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERevolutionaries%20were%20inspired%20by%20Chandrashekar%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20(1906-1931)%20poem%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDushmanon%20ki%20goliyan%20ka%20hum%20samna%20karenge%3Cbr%3E%5CnAzad%20hi%20rahe%20hai%2C%20azaad%20hi%20rahenge%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20will%20face%20the%20bullets%20of%20the%20enemy%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20have%20been%20free%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20free%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20equally%20motivated%20by%20the%20poet%20of%20revolution%20Josh%20Malihabadi%20(1894-1982)%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMera%20naara%2C%20inquilab%20O%20inquilab%20O%20inquilab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20slogan%20is%20revolution%2C%20revolution%2C%20revolution%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20can%20we%20differentiate%20between%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20poetry%20and%20poets%3F%20Both%20passionately%20desired%20freedom%20to%20make%20our%20own%20destiny%2C%20and%20both%20wrote%20amazing%20poetry%20to%20capture%20political%20resistance%20as%20well%20as%20their%20dreams%20of%20independence.%20They%20were%20supported%20by%20writers%20and%20theatre%20and%20film%20actors.%20Bhisham%20and%20Balraj%20Sahni%2C%20Prithviraj%2C%20Raj%20and%20Shammi%20Kapoor%20and%20a%20number%20of%20stars%20including%20the%20debonair%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20as%20well%20poets%20Jan%20Nisar%20Akhtar%2C%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%2C%20and%20Sardar%20Jafri%20among%20others%2C%20spoke%20up%20and%20marched%20against%20communalism%2C%20poverty%20and%20social%20oppression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20progressives%20taught%20us%20that%20society%20has%20to%20look%20outwards%20towards%20imperialism%2C%20but%20it%20also%20has%20to%20look%20inward%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20many%20contradictions%2C%20oppressions%2C%20and%20tyrannies%20of%20our%20own%20society.%20Liberation%20is%20incomplete%20unless%20Indians%20liberate%20themselves%20from%20a%20caste-bound%2C%20religiously%20bigoted%20and%20patriarchal%20society.%20They%20radicalised%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20radicalised%20literature%20and%20poetry%20because%20they%20showed%20Indians%20another%20way%20beyond%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20binary%3A%20the%20domain%20of%20sensitivity%20and%20solidarity%20forged%20by%20the%20overpowering%20need%20to%20tackle%20the%20ills%20that%20beset%20the%20human%20condition.%20Human%20beings%20cannot%20be%20essentialised%20and%20reduced%20to%20their%20religious%20identity.%20They%20are%20capable%20of%20walking%20another%20path%3A%20solidarity%20with%20the%20oppressed%2C%20compassion%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20sensitivity%20to%20the%20sufferings%20of%20their%20people.%20The%20Indian%20constitution%20was%20born%20out%20of%20these%20sentiments.%20Recollect%20that%20fraternity%20is%20stated%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20objectives%20of%20our%20secular%2C%20socialist%2C%20democratic%20Republic%20in%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20time%20came%20for%20our%20leaders%2C%20who%20had%20passed%20through%20the%20fire%20of%20struggle%2C%20to%20write%20the%20constitution%2C%20India%20was%20Partitioned.%20Destruction%20and%20death%20formed%20the%20backdrop%20to%20the%20making%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20deliberations%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20put%20the%20matter%20in%20a%20nutshell.%20On%20December%2011%2C%201946%2C%20he%20stated%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Constituent%20Assembly%20is%20meeting%20at%20a%20most%20critical%20time.%20We%20all%20know%20that%20other%20constituent%20assemblies%2C%20whenever%20and%20wherever%20they%20met%2C%20were%20confronted%20with%20similar%20difficulties.%20They%20had%20also%20to%20contend%20with%20internal%20differences%20which%20were%20placed%20before%20them%20with%20great%20vehemence.%20Many%20of%20these%20constituent%20assemblies%20were%20held%20amidst%20strife%20and%20bloodshed%3B%20even%20their%20proceedings%20were%20conducted%20amidst%20quarrels%20and%20fights.%20Their%20members%20joined%20together%20and%20with%20courage%2C%20kindness%2C%20generosity%2C%20tolerance%20and%20regard%20for%20one%20another%E2%80%99s%20feelings%20framed%20constitutions%20which%20were%20then%20readily%20accepted%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20countries%20for%20which%20they%20were%20framed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20specific%20mandate%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20to%20create%20a%20constitution%20in%20a%20spirit%20of%20courage%2C%20kindness%2C%20generosity%2C%20tolerance%2C%20regard%20for%20each%20one%20another%E2%80%99s%20feelings%20and%20solidarity.%20The%20task%20was%20difficult.%20The%20horrors%20of%20the%20Partition%20had%20reduced%20Indians%20to%20their%20primeval%20identities%20%E2%80%93%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20and%20Muslim.%20The%20miracle%20is%20that%20a%20democratic%20constitution%20that%20provided%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities%20was%20written%20amidst%20the%20debris%20of%20destroyed%20homes%2C%20workplaces%2C%20temples%2C%20gurudwaras%2C%20and%20mosques.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%209%2C%201946%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20met%20in%20the%20central%20hall%20of%20the%20magnificently%20elegant%20and%20famed%20circular%20building%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20after%20independence%20became%20India%E2%80%99s%20(first)%20Parliament%2C%20to%20draft%20a%20constitution%20for%20a%20people%20headed%20towards%20independence.%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20took%20care%20to%20emphasise%20that%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20not%20a%20gift%20of%20the%20colonial%20government.%20It%20was%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20number%20of%20initiatives%20taken%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%3B%20it%20was%20the%20product%20of%20the%20intellectual%20labour%20of%20Indian%20jurists%2C%20public%20intellectuals%2C%20and%20creators%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20Collectively%20these%20initiatives%20had%20smote%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20a%20democratic%20polity%20onto%20a%20political%20stone%20since%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20twentieth%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIntroducing%20the%20Objectives%20Resolution%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20December%2013%2C%201946%2C%20Nehru%20memorably%20remarked%20in%20his%20inimitably%20elegant%20prose%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwords%20are%20magic%20things%20often%20enough%2C%20but%20even%20the%20magic%20of%20words%20sometimes%20cannot%20convey%20the%20magic%20of%20the%20human%20spirit%20and%20of%20a%20Nation%E2%80%99s%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20resolution%20cannot%20convey%20this%20passion%2C%20continued%20Nehru%2C%20it%20very%20feebly%20tells%20the%20world%20of%20what%20we%20have%20dreamt%20of%20and%20what%20we%20now%20hope%20to%20achieve.%20What%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20constitution%20wished%20to%20achieve%20was%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20stupendous%20transformation%20of%20society%2C%20the%20polity%20and%20of%20the%20economy%20after%20200%20years%20of%20colonial%20rule.%20The%20soul%20of%20the%20constitution%20was%20the%20charter%20of%20Fundamental%20Rights%2C%20the%20institutionalisation%20of%20checks%20on%20the%20exercise%20of%20power%2C%20and%20popular%20sovereignty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F28152458%2FGroup-photograph-of-members-of-the-Constituent-Assembly-of-India-Legislative-1949.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F28152458%2FGroup-photograph-of-members-of-the-Constituent-Assembly-of-India-Legislative-1949.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F28152458%2FGroup-photograph-of-members-of-the-Constituent-Assembly-of-India-Legislative-1949-300x174.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F28152458%2FGroup-photograph-of-members-of-the-Constituent-Assembly-of-India-Legislative-1949-1024x594.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-500779%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGroup%20photograph%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20India%20(Legislative)%2C%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20day%20the%20constitution%20was%20promulgated%20on%20January%2026%2C%201950%2C%20was%20tinged%20by%20sorrow%20at%20the%20tragedies%20of%20the%20Partition.%20The%20makers%20were%20also%20overcome%20by%20the%20prime%20responsibility%20of%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20constitution%3A%20to%20bring%20together%20a%20divided%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20Preamble%20embodies%20the%20ideals%20of%20a%20generation%20that%20fought%20for%20independence.%20It%20was%20designed%20for%20generations%20that%20were%20to%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20ideals%20do%20people%20who%20want%20to%20rewrite%20the%20constitution%20represent%3F%20What%20is%20their%20ideology%20or%20their%20experiences%20of%20solidarity%20with%20the%20oppressed%2C%20or%20even%20their%20understanding%20of%20what%20India%20stands%20for%20%E2%80%93%20pluralism%20and%20tolerance%2C%20secularism%20and%20democracy%2C%20freedom%2C%20equality%20and%20justice%20for%20every%20citizen%3F%20The%20record%20of%20the%20current%20power%20elite%20is%20not%20too%20encouraging%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20democracy%20that%20the%20constitution%20institutionalises%20and%20protects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-those-demanding-a-new-constitution-are-fighting-for-a-less-equal-india%5C%22%3EAll%20Those%20Demanding%20a%20New%20Constitution%20Are%20Fighting%20for%20a%20Less%20Equal%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20will%20happen%20if%20the%20constitution%20is%20rewritten%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShall%20we%20think%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20us%20if%20the%20constitution%20is%20abolished%20or%20rewritten%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20ruling%20class%3F%20For%20one%2C%20we%20will%20be%20saddled%20with%20a%20leadership%20that%20is%20not%20of%20our%20choice%2C%20which%20is%20not%20even%20nominally%20accountable%20to%20the%20political%20public%2C%20and%20one%20that%20disdains%20popular%20opinion.%20Now%20we%20know%20that%20even%20if%20we%20elect%20a%20morally%20callous%20leadership%2C%20it%20has%20to%20come%20back%20to%20us%20after%20five%20years%20begging%20for%20votes.%20There%20have%20been%20times%20when%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20given%20a%20fitting%20reply%20to%20authoritarian%20governments.%20In%201975%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20government%20declared%20an%20Internal%20Emergency.%20Civil%20liberties%20were%20suspended%2C%20the%20courts%20and%20the%20bureaucracy%20lost%20autonomy%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20political%20opponents%20were%20jailed.%20In%201977%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20lifted%20the%20Emergency%20and%20called%20for%20elections.%20The%20Congress%20was%20spectacularly%20defeated%2C%20and%20she%20not%20only%20lost%20her%20constituency%20but%20also%20her%20deposit.%20The%20people%20of%20India%20knew%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20their%20rights%20during%20the%20period%20had%20violated%20our%20democratic%20constitution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20imagine%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20constitution%20was%20rewritten%20without%20the%20Chapter%20on%20Fundamental%20Rights.%20We%20will%20be%20left%20helpless%2C%20vulnerable%20to%20state%20power%20and%20to%20the%20power%20of%20the%20dominant%20classes.%20We%20will%20live%20in%20a%20state%20of%20anomie%20and%20fear%20straight%20out%20of%20George%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E1984%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20will%20be%20subjected%20to%20laws%20that%20are%20neither%20limited%20by%20propriety%2C%20nor%20by%20legislative%20procedures.%20Today%2C%20even%20if%20the%20ruling%20party%20can%20push%20through%20legislation%20without%20submitting%20Bills%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20committees%20because%20it%20is%20in%20a%20majority%2C%20we%20know%20the%20procedure%20%E2%80%93%20and%20consequently%20the%20law%20%E2%80%93%20is%20unjust.%20We%20know%20because%20the%20constitution%20establishes%20a%20criterion%20to%20judge%20which%20law%20is%20or%20is%20not%20justifiable.%20We%20will%20lose%20this%20criterion%2C%20the%20guide%20to%20good%20legislation%2C%20and%20the%20measure%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20India%20which%20still%20remains%20short%20of%20being%20a%20good%20society%2C%20our%20dreams%20of%20freedom%2C%20our%20aspirations%20to%20be%20as%20equal%20as%20other%20fellow%20citizens%2C%20and%20our%20passionate%20desire%20for%20justice%20will%20remain%20unfulfilled.%20We%20will%20become%20subjects%20of%20an%20authoritarian%20state%2C%20no%20longer%20citizens%20of%20a%20proud%20Republic.%20We%20need%20our%20constitution%20simply%20because%20palpable%20checks%20on%20the%20propensity%20of%20governments%20to%20exercise%20uncontrollable%20power%20are%20necessary.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20if%20a%20constitution%20that%20is%20written%20by%20a%20party%20that%20is%20dedicated%20to%20majoritarianism%20will%20ever%20think%20of%20including%20justice%20within%20the%20Preamble.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20worry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fneera-chandhoke%5C%22%3ENeera%20Chandhoke%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693043828000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F15105244%2Fconstitution-of-india.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fconstitution-mass-movement-rights-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20constitution%20institutionalises%20the%20ideals%20of%20democracy.%20Left%20to%20itself%2C%20democracy%20can%20go%20completely%20haywire.%20It%20can%20be%20reduced%20to%20elections%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0as%20it%20has%20been%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%20Without%20a%20constitution%2C%20we%20will%20never%20know%20that%20there%20is%20more%20to%20democracy%20than%20just%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fconstitution-mass-movement-rights-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hermoso%20v%20Rubiales%3A%20Who%20said%20what%20in%20World%20Cup%20kiss%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693043460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-spain-hermoso-rubiales_6263117.png%3F20230826155419%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvictims-of-an-aggression-and-a-witch-hunt-who-said-what-in-world-cup-kiss-row-between-luis-rubiales-and-jenni-hermoso-12947809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20should%20have%20been%20a%20celebration%20of%20Spanish%20football%20has%20turned%20into%20an%20almighty%20row%20between%20the%20women's%20team%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2280%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvictims-of-an-aggression-and-a-witch-hunt-who-said-what-in-world-cup-kiss-row-between-luis-rubiales-and-jenni-hermoso-12947809%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvictims-of-an-aggression-and-a-witch-hunt-who-said-what-in-world-cup-kiss-row-between-luis-rubiales-and-jenni-hermoso-12947809%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvictims-of-an-aggression-and-a-witch-hunt-who-said-what-in-world-cup-kiss-row-between-luis-rubiales-and-jenni-hermoso-12947809%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20B.%20SRK%20to%20reunite%20after%2017%20years!%22%2C%22content%22%3