0with%20joy%20and%20pride%20as%20he%20interacted%20with%20the%20little%20girl.%20Little%20did%20she%20know%20that%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20in%20a%20remote%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20schoolboy%20trembled%20as%20his%20teacher%20egged%20his%20classmates%20to%20slap%20him.%20Though%20his%20face%20was%20streaked%20with%20tears%2C%20the%20teacher%20taunted%20a%20classmate%20for%20not%20raining%20blows%20hard%20enough%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20boy%20being%20slapped%20was%20Muslim%20and%20that%20the%20teacher%20made%20a%20sweeping%2C%20derogatory%20reference%20to%20Muslims%2C%20only%20added%20to%20the%20horrendous%20nature%20of%C2%A0%20the%20video%20seen%20on%20social%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20public%20outrage%2C%20the%20police%20visited%20the%20school%20in%20Muzzafarnagar%20district%20and%20said%20it%20would%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20Of%20course%2C%20had%20the%20victim%20been%20a%20Hindu%20and%20the%20perpetrator%20a%20Muslim%2C%20the%20teacher%20would%20have%20been%20promptly%20arrested%20and%20their%20home%20bulldozed%20by%20an%20eager%20state%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20too%20scared%20or%20weary%20to%20initiate%20action%20is%20emblematic%20of%20the%20eroding%20trust%20between%20minorities%20and%20the%20legal%20institutions%20responsible%20for%20protecting%20them.%20He%20took%20the%20only%20recourse%20available%20by%20forbidding%20his%20son%20to%20attend%20school.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20result%20that%20those%20consumed%20with%20the%20bigotry%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20hoped%20for.%20This%20is%20precisely%20what%20happened%20after%20the%20%E2%80%98hijab%20controversy%E2%80%99%20in%20Karnataka%20that%20led%20to%20many%20Muslim%20families%20discontinuing%20their%20daughters%E2%80%99%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fcareer-and-campus%2Ftop-news%2F2023%2F02%2F15%2Fdrastic-cut-in-central-scholarship-fellowship-funds.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20many%20of%20the%20scholarships%20earmarked%20for%20minorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20the%20path%20to%20their%20empowerment%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20flames%20of%20hatred%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20actively%20fanned%20since%202014%20are%20now%20threatening%20to%20singe%20the%20safe%20sanctuary%20of%20our%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20so-called%20mother%20of%20democracy%20get%20to%20this%20abhorrent%20point%3F%20As%20if%20engineered%20riots%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20modus%20operandi%20to%20sow%20division%20now%20includes%20propaganda%20through%20movies%20steeped%20in%20disinformation%20and%20demonisation%20of%20Muslims.%20Otherwise%20what%20explains%20a%20slew%20of%20anti-Muslim%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20files%2C%2072%20Hoorain%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EKerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20promoted%20by%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%3F%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20vilified%20all%20Kashmiri%20Muslims%2C%20was%20recently%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20official%20prize%20for%20%E2%80%98national%20integration%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20country%20we%20have%20become%2C%20shocking%20incidents%20against%20minorities%20which%20should%20have%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20shame%20for%20everyone%20are%20instead%20being%20glorified%20and%20turned%20into%20symbols%20of%20national%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20as%20we%20approach%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20general%20election%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20will%20only%20encourage%20such%20incidents%20which%20are%20a%20blot%20on%20the%20collective%20conscious%20of%20a%20nation%20that%20was%20once%20led%20by%20Gandhiji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20had%20I%20imagined%20that%20the%20poison%20spewed%20by%20BJP%20would%20singe%20even%20children.%20While%20the%20dogged%20determination%20of%20our%20scientists%20ensured%20India%20landed%20successfully%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20our%20vitriolic%20politicians%20are%20hell%20bent%20on%20taking%20us%20back%20to%20the%20dark%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20abysmal%2010-year%20performance%2C%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20its%20large%20election%20machinery%20will%20rely%20primarily%20on%20religious%20polarisation%20and%20the%20stoking%20of%20communal%20fires%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%202024.%20Their%20reliance%20on%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20other%20government%20agencies%20to%20browbeat%20their%20opponents%20may%20not%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20BJPs%20nervousness%20after%20its%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%2C%20all%20the%20sluice%20gates%20have%20been%20opened%20regardless%20of%20where%20the%20hate%20ends%20up.%20And%20now%20the%20poison%20has%20reached%20our%20schools.%20As%20I%20write%20this%2C%20I%20wonder%20what%20will%20it%20take%20for%20my%20country%20to%20awaken%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693041617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20did%20the%20so-called%20'mother%20of%20democracy'%20get%20to%20this%20abhorrent%20point%3F%20What%20will%20it%20take%20for%20my%20country%20to%20awaken%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A139%2C%22canonicalUrl%