0in%20the%20society%20that%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20an%20education%20teacher%2C%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20is%20teaching%20the%20lesson%20of%20religious%20hatred%20since%20childhood%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20security%20personnel%20RPF%20jawan%2C%20Chetan%20Kumar%2C%20is%20killing%20innocent%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20also%20questioned%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20and%20its%20chief%20Priyank%20Kangoo.%20As%20a%20first%20response%2C%20Kangoo%20had%20insisted%20that%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20be%20removed%20from%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20video%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%20where%20a%20teacher%20is%20asking%20her%20students%20to%20slap%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20is%20a%20product%20of%20the%20last%209%20years.%20The%20message%20being%20drilled%20into%20the%20minds%20of%20little%20children%20is%20that%20one%20can%20beat%20up%20%26amp%3B%20humiliate%20a%20Muslim%20without%20any%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20(%40asadowaisi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasadowaisi%2Fstatus%2F1695295517628968985%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20after%20the%20FIR%20had%20been%20filed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Flodge-fir-up-teacher-kids-hit-muslim-student-ncpcr-muzaffarnagar-ssp-8910659%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20NCPCR%20has%20told%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20SSP%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20Tyagi%20under%20Section%2017%20(child%20being%20subjected%