0of%20the%20loan%2C%20I%20established%20my%20own%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20workshop.%20However%2C%20in%202014%2C%20my%20workshop%20suffered%20complete%20destruction%20due%20to%20the%20floods.%20Unfortunately%2C%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20insurance%20coverage%20and%20the%20burden%20of%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20repay%20this%20loan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20floods%2C%20there%20was%20no%20support%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20help%20the%20artisans%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet%3B%20rather%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sudden%20rise%20in%20the%20interest%20rates%20on%20the%20loans%20taken%20before%20the%20floods.%20This%20further%20led%20to%20more%20problems%20for%20the%20artisans.%20Thus%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20resources%20and%20loss%20of%20finished%20goods%20set%20the%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20industry%20back%20to%20the%20point%20where%20they%20could%20no%20longer%20pay%20interest%20on%20the%20previously%20taken%20loans%20or%20sustain%20a%20livelihood%20with%20the%20minimal%20income%20they%20managed%20to%20earn.%20All%20of%20this%20forced%20many%20artisans%20to%20leave%20the%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20industry%20and%20move%20to%20safer%2C%20better-earning%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasir%20Shah*%2C%20a%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20exporter%20for%20nearly%2030%20years%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lack%20of%20insurance%20coverage%20for%20the%20artists%20resulted%20in%20substantial%20losses%20during%20the%20floods.%20Consequently%2C%20many%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20artists%20had%20to%20explore%20alternative%20means%20of%20livelihood.%20Some%20turned%20to%20selling%20vegetables%2C%20while%20others%20found%20employment%20as%20ATM%20guards%20or%20security%20personnel%20at%20various%20tourist%20parks.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20only%20around%2020%25%20of%20the%20artists%20remain%20associated%20with%20this%20craft.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%20catastrophe%2C%20political%20instability%20and%20violent%20contentions%20in%20the%20state%20during%20the%20period%20between%202016%20and%202019%20caused%20a%20further%20decline%20in%20the%20craft%20as%20the%20influx%20of%20tourists%20and%20their%20demands%20plunged.%20The%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20tourism%20and%20exports%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20quoted%20by%20one%20of%20the%20exporters%20we%20interviewed%2C%20the%20annual%20turnover%20of%20the%20export%20line%20of%20Kashmir%20fell%20from%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%2C%20all%20due%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20pandemic-induced%20lockdowns.%20Such%20a%20large%20fall%20in%20exports%20further%20deteriorated%20the%20market%20conditions%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20the%20art%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20impact%20of%20commercialisation%20on%20the%20paper%20mache%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20hardly%20any%20help%20from%20the%20government%2C%20the%20artisans%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20depend%20on%20bulk%20export%20orders%20to%20support%20their%20livelihood%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20they%20are%20hardly%20able%20to%20manage%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Saad%20Naqash*%2C%2037%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChanges%20in%20the%20craft%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20have%20been%20significant%2C%20driven%20by%20consumer%20demands.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20traditional%20design%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20has%20undergone%20a%20complete%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25165438%2Fimage-1247.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25165438%2Fimage-1247.png%20755w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25165438%2Fimage-1247-300x164.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669842%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22413%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20production%20of%20the%20art%20is%20largely%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20requirements%20of%20buyers%20abroad%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20traditional%20designs%20(which%20consist%20of%20motifs)%20have%20started%20disappearing%20from%20the%20mainstream%20market.%20%E2%80%9CNowadays%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saad*%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20focus%20is%20on%20mass%20production%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20products%20in%20bulk%20quantities%2C%20sometimes%20reaching%20thousands.%20However%2C%20this%20shift%20towards%20quantity%20over%20quality%20has%20had%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20overall%20craftsmanship%20and%20authenticity%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commercialisation%20and%20heavy%20focus%20on%20completing%20bulk%20orders%20have%20led%20to%20a%20newer%20generation%20of%20artists%20who%20are%20less%20patient%20and%20less%20respectful%20of%20the%20art.%20What%20was%20once%20considered%20art%20has%20shifted%20merely%20to%20%E2%80%9Cproducts%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20industry%20witnessed%20a%20decline%20in%20its%20originality%20and%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirza%20Ghulam%20Hyder%2C%20a%20national%20awardee%20for%20his%20art%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbSc7ESpn1RI%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20his%20displeasure%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20products%20are%20mainly%20used%20for%20advertisements%20in%20foreign%20countries.%20People%20have%20now%20started%20using%20various%20kinds%20of%20material%20such%20as%20earthen%20pots%20which%20are%20not%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9.%20I%20feel%20very%20sad%20when%20I%20look%20at%20how%20the%20government%20is%20ruining%20this%20craft%20by%20preparing%20new%20generations%20in%20various%20training%20centres%2C%20which%20is%20not%20real%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20work.%20They%20are%20defaming%20this%20craft.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2tYXRlKZRZI%3Fsi%3DqIaVIXdGqocTeUl3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20commercialisation%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20has%20provided%20artists%20with%20new%20but%20modest%20income%20streams%2C%20it%20comes%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20original%20art%20form%20that%20demands%20time%20and%20patience%20%E2%80%93%20qualities%20often%20lacking%20in%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20role%20of%20intermediaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20continued%20commercialisation%20and%20international%20demand%20for%20the%20craft%20from%20the%20West%20inevitably%20required%20the%20local%20artisans%20to%20depend%20on%20middlemen%20as%20a%20medium%20of%20bulk%20export.%20This%20is%20primarily%20because%20the%20artisans%20lack%20the%20resources%20to%20export%20the%20products%20directly.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20have%20to%20rely%20heavily%20on%20exporters%20to%20help%20them%20earn%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20conflicting%20opinions%20on%20how%20these%20exporters%20contribute%20to%20keeping%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20alive.%20While%20some%20artisans%20believe%20that%20they%20get%20a%20fair%20price%20from%20the%20exporters%20for%20their%20products%2C%20others%20do%20not.%20Instead%2C%20others%20believe%20that%20the%20competition%20between%20the%20exporters%20causes%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20raw%20materials%20for%20production.%20So%2C%20while%20the%20selling%20price%20remains%20the%20same%20and%20as%20the%20cost%20price%20increases%2C%20it%20is%20the%20artisans%20who%20must%20face%20the%20music%20and%20endure%20the%20difference%2C%20resulting%20in%20less%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fvx8Ypz8rif8%3Fsi%3DGRRLUy3ltEKjXTn5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuqsood%20Ahmad%20Ganie%20sheds%20more%20light%20on%20this%20situation%20by%20comparing%20the%20costs%20of%20raw%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20balls%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20makers%20of%20raw%20material%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20bargain%20for%20a%20better%20price%20because%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20individuals%20are%20now%20available%20who%20can%20make%20bases%20of%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20products.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20raw%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20balls%20for%20%3Cem%3Echith%20wala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(made%20of%20raw%20material)%20belonging%20to%20the%20Sunni%20community%20has%20increased%20from%20Rs%208%20to%20Rs%2019%20from%202019%20to%202023%20but%20the%20cost%20for%20us%20who%20give%20the%20final%20touch%20to%20these%20products%20has%20decreased.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArtists%20like%20us%20are%20not%20getting%20their%20due%20recognition%20and%20amount.%20Another%20example%20here%2C%20last%20year%20the%20labour%20cost%20per%20box%20was%20Rs%2015%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20camel%20colour%20tubes%20was%20Rs%206%2C%20but%20now%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20same%20colour%20is%20Rs%2030%20and%20the%20labour%20cost%20of%20the%20box%20is%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExporters%20believe%20that%20while%20government%20officials%20claim%20to%20have%20helped%20the%20overworked%20artisans%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20quite%20the%20opposite.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20small%20artisans%20find%20no%20relaxation%20in%20taxes%2C%20namely%20GST.%20They%20have%20to%20pay%20extra%20money%20for%20the%20raw%20materials%2C%20which%20further%20drives%20up%20the%20cost%20price%20while%20they%20receive%20no%20return%20on%20the%20taxes%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20GST%20number.%20Even%20with%20higher%20expenses%2C%20the%20selling%20price%20for%20the%20products%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20leaving%20less%20profit%20margin%20for%20both%20the%20artisans%20and%20the%20exporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%2C%20the%20exporters%20face%20difficulties%20due%20to%20inconsistent%20transport%20charges%20and%20stoppage%20at%20customs%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20which%20can%20easily%20be%20solved%20by%20government%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20larger%20area%20of%20concern%20is%20the%20disparity%20between%20the%20earnings%20of%20the%20artisans%20and%20those%20of%20exporters.%20Not%20only%20do%20the%20artisans%20believe%20that%20exporters%20give%20them%20low%20wages%20for%20the%20products%2C%20but%20they%20also%20give%20this%20minimal%20wage%20in%20instalments%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20the%20artisans%20to%20survive.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20intervention%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20aid%20the%20underpaid%20artisans%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20a%20monopolistic%20situation%20has%20come%20up%20where%20artists%20remain%20with%20limited%20options%20for%20selling%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3Cem%3ENames%20of%20all%20respondents%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect%20their%20identity%20and%20maintain%20anonymity.%20The%20authors%20would%20like%20to%20especially%20thank%20Rekha%20Pachauri%20and%20Meera%20Shirodkar%20for%20their%20assistance%20with%20fieldwork%2C%20interviews%20and%20the%20audio-video%20documentation%20of%20the%20study.%20Without%20their%20support%2C%20this%20study%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible.%20All%20photographs%20are%20credited%20to%20them%20and%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%