ic%20position%2C%20as%20a%20large%20emerging%20market%20economy%20with%20a%20demographically%20positive%20employment%20base%2C%20offers%20greater%20optimism%20than%20some%20of%20the%20other%20emerging%20markets%20and%20the%20more%20industrially%20advanced%20nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20since%20it%20was%20elected%2C%20has%20often%20harped%20on%20this%20signalling%20message%20to%20project%20%E2%80%98positive%20optimism%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98strength%E2%80%99%20for%20those%20betting%20big%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20rising%20growth%20potential%20as%20against%20other%20nations.%20Efforts%20by%20foreign%20investors%20and%20firms%20to%20decouple%20from%20China%20did%20offer%20an%20opportunity%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20growing%20potential%20of%20the%20Indian%20market.%20However%2C%20not%20all%20has%20been%20well%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20we%20get%20closer%20into%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20cycle%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20plausible%20to%20hear%20a%20lot%20more%20rhetorical%20activism%2C%20hype%20over%20reality%2C%20fiction%20over%20fact%2C%20around%20what%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20did%20right%20%E2%80%93%20in%20making%20India%20a%20%E2%80%98shining%E2%80%99%20star%20amidst%20a%20universe%20of%20struggling%2C%20recession-affected%2C%20debt-ballooned%20economies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20Indian%20economy%E2%80%99s%20own%20macro%20numbers%2C%20however%2C%20paints%20a%20different%20picture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20more%20cause%20for%20trouble%20and%20skepticism%20than%20optimism.%20Yes%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20potential%20is%20massive%2C%20but%20on%20evidence%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20much%20optimism%20or%20hope%20in%20the%20current%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20t