utam-Yadav-1692620841-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327817%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Gautam%20discovered%20his%20sexuality.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20these%20sessions%20that%20the%20counsellor%20suggested%20that%20Gautam%20be%20tested%20for%20HIV%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20multiple%20sexual%20partners.%20And%20though%20he%20had%20no%20symptoms%2C%20he%20tested%20positive%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20when%20people%20come%20to%20know%20that%20they%20are%20positive%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20comes%20to%20their%20mind%20is%20how%20long%20they%20are%20going%20to%20live.%20I%20also%20did%20not%20know%20how%20long%20I%20would%20survive.%20Questions%20like%20%E2%80%98Who%20will%20take%20care%20of%20my%20parents%20after%20my%20death%3F%E2%80%99%20started%20worrying%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20it%20took%20him%20a%20year%20to%20understand%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20worry.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20upset%20and%20depressed%20in%20that%20period%2C%20but%20my%20fear%20went%20away%20when%20I%20started%20meeting%20people%20who%20are%20HIV-positive.%20They%20made%20me%20understand%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20worry%20if%20I%20took%20medicines%20on%20time.%20Treatment%20adherence%20is%20important%20to%20lead%20a%20normal%20life.%20Today%2C%20I%20do%20not%20even%20feel%20that%20I%20am%20positive.%20It%20hardly%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20he%20was%20still%20accepting%20the%20reality%2C%20Gautam%20was%20not%20spared%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97559%2Fhiv-aids-act-positive-news-legislation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estigma%20and%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20very%20close%20and%20trustworthy%20friend.%20When%20I%20revealed%20my%20status%20to%20him%2C%20he%20was%20empathetic.%20After%20a%20week%2C%20he%20organised%20a%20dinner%20party%20and%20invited%20me.%20But%20before%20I%20reached%20there%2C%20he%20had%20informed%20everyone%20to%20be%20cautious%20as%20I%20was%20HIV%20positive.%20That%20was%20heartbreaking%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recalls%20the%20bullying%20he%20faces%20on%20social%20media.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20use%20dating%20applications%2C%20people%20write%20to%20me%20from%20blank%20profiles%20and%20ask%20why%20I%E2%80%99m%20spreading%20AIDS%2C%20or%20that%20I%20should%20not%20be%20on%20dating%20platforms.%20People%20like%20me%20should%20%E2%80%98die%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20very%20triggering%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Delhi's%20Gautam%20has%20been%20living%20with%20HIV%20since%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-2-1692620944-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327821%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20Gautam%20has%20been%20living%20with%20HIV%20since%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20Gautam%20has%20not%20only%20learned%20to%20live%20with%20HIV%2C%20but%20also%20conquered%20the%20stigma%20and%20fear%20that%20comes%20alongside.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%2015%20years%20since%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20living%20with%20HIV%20and%20working%20for%20the%20community.%20The%20work%20has%20helped%20me%20gain%20comprehensive%20knowledge%20about%20the%20disease%2C%20and%20awareness%20has%20made%20my%20life%20easier.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20nothing%20wrong%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%20I%20lead%20a%20healthy%20and%20normal%20life.%20Over%20these%20years%2C%20nothing%20has%20changed.%20All%20I%20have%20to%20do%20is%20ensure%20that%20I%20take%20medicines%20on%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20people%20living%20with%20HIV%20should%20know%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20several%20programmes%20on%20prevention%20and%20awareness%20of%20HIV%2C%20Gautam%20says%20that%20the%20stigma%20associated%20with%20the%20disease%20prevails.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20think%20that%20they%20can%20get%20HIV%20by%20being%20around%20people%20who%20are%20positive.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20even%20on%20television%2C%20if%20there%20is%20an%20advertisement%20on%20HIV%2C%20we%20immediately%20switch%20the%20channel%2C%20we%20do%20not%20bother%20to%20know%20about%20the%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20you%20may%20not%20have%20anyone%20in%20your%20family%20or%20friends%20with%20HIV%2C%20but%20you%20never%20know%20about%20the%20future.%20People%20need%20to%20improve%20their%20knowledge%20about%20HIV%20and%20understand%20it%20is%20just%20a%20disease%20for%20which%20you%20need%20timely%20medication%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhat-people-living-with-HIV-should-know-1692624549.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhat-people-living-with-HIV-should-know-1692624549.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhat-people-living-with-HIV-should-know-1692624549-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhat-people-living-with-HIV-should-know-1692624549-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhat-people-living-with-HIV-should-know-1692624549-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhat-people-living-with-HIV-should-know-1692624549-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327842%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Gautam%20has%20learned%20many%20tools%20that%20have%20helped%20him%20lead%20his%20life%20alongside%20having%20HIV.%20He%20shares%20some%20valuable%20insights%20and%20helpful%20advice%20for%20PLHIV%20based%20on%20his%20own%20experiences%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20tested%20every%20six%20months%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20when%20a%20person%20should%20test%20for%20HIV%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20takes%205-10%20years%20for%20symptoms%20of%20HIV%20%5Bfever%2C%20chills%2C%20fatigue%5D%20to%20appear.%20If%20someone%20is%20sexually%20active%20and%20has%20multiple%20partners%2C%20they%20should%20get%20tested%20every%20six%20months.%20If%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263464%2Ftamil-nadu-positive-women-network-hiv-aids-care-cheap-treatment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etest%20positive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20should%20not%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20the%20end%20of%20life.%20You%20must%20have%20patience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnect%20with%20the%20right%20network%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20you%20test%20positive%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20related%20people%20and%20organisations.%20Gautam%20advises%20that%20you%20can%20call%20the%20national%20helpline%20at%201097%20to%20understand%20about%20HIV%2FAIDS%2C%20or%20visit%20ICTC%20(Integrated%20Counseling%20%26amp%3B%20Testing%20Center)%20to%20render%20information%20about%20HIV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstand%20the%20difference%20between%20HIV%20and%20AIDS.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CHIV%20is%20the%20virus%20that%20causes%20AIDS%2C%20which%20is%20life-threatening.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20that%20one%20will%20end%20up%20having%20AIDS.%20With%20proper%20medication%2C%20that%20condition%20is%20avoidable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20medicines%20on%20time.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20eat%20whatever%20you%20want.%20Be%20cautious%20of%20the%20timings%20of%20the%20medicine%20intake.%20The%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282114%2Fsocial-worker-helps-hiv-positive-pregnant-women-get-medication%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20medicines%20for%20HIV%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20known%20as%20life-saving%20drugs.%20You%20need%20to%20take%20them%20till%20you%20are%20alive.%20If%20you%20stop%20taking%20them%2C%20it%20would%20result%20in%20a%20weakened%20immune%20system%20and%20AIDS%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20do%20if%20viral%20load%20is%20less%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fhealth-topics%2Fhiv-aids%23tab%3Dtab_1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Health%20Organization%20%3C%2Fa%3E(WHO)%2C%20if%20the%20viral%20load%20in%20the%20blood%20is%2050%20copies%2Fml%2C%20it%20means%20the%20virus%20is%20at%20undetectable%20levels.%20If%20viral%20load%20is%20greater%20than%201%2C000%20copies%2Fml%2C%20it%20is%20an%20indicator%20of%20inadequate%20treatment%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20says%20that%20if%20a%20positive%20person%20has%20a%20viral%20load%20of%20less%20than%2050%20copies%2Fml%2C%20the%20HIV%20would%20usually%20be%20undetectable.%20Regardless%2C%20they%20should%20still%20practise%20safe%20sex.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20you%20are%20undetectable%20and%20non-transmissible%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20we%20do%20not%20encourage%20you%20to%20have%20unprotected%20sexual%20intercourse.%20It%20can%20lead%20to%20sexually%20transmitted%20diseases%20that%20are%20more%20harmful%20than%20HIV%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20says%20that%20people%20living%20with%20HIV%20should%20not%20let%20the%20virus%20decide%20how%20they%20lead%20their%20lives.%20He%20believes%20that%20life%20is%20changing%20in%20a%20positive%20way%20for%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20able%20to%20assist%20many%20people%2C%20even%20those%20who%20were%20suicidal.%20The%20impact%20keeps%20me%20motivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20also%20represented%20my%20country%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20as%20a%20board%20member%20for%20the%20Youth%20Advisory%20Forum.%20So%20far%2C%20I%20have%20visited%20more%20than%2025%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Thailand%20for%20conferences%20and%20I%20was%20part%20of%20several%20organisations%20like%20Hamsafar%20Trust%20and%20UNESCO.%20I%20have%20been%20doing%20this%20work%20very%20selflessly%20and%20I%20would%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20community%20had%20I%20not%20been%20positive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1657057%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520per%2520the%2520latest%2520HIV%2C37%2525%2520between%25202010%2520and%25202019.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHIV%2FAIDS%20Patients%20in%20India%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3EPublished%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20on%2020%20September%202020%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692624391000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Yadav%2C%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20HIV%20in%202009%2C%20has%20been%20working%20to%20fight%20the%20stigma%20and%20myths%20associated%20with%20the%20illness%20for%2015%20years.%20He%20narrates%20his%20life%20as%20a%20PLHIV%2C%20and%20what%20he%20wishes%20people%20knew%20about%20the%20disease.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20the%20Heart%20of%20Chikmagalur%2C%20Couple%20Turns%20British-Era%20Home%20into%20a%20Tranquil%20Heritage%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20who%20steps%20into%20the%20serene%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Estate%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Chikmagalur%20homestay%20property%20run%20by%20Susmitha%20and%20Shreedev%20in%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20an%20enriching%20experience%20awaits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bungalow%2C%20first%20built%20in%201904%2C%20has%20witnessed%20quite%20the%20evolution.%20Right%20from%20the%20city%20being%20an%20isolated%20spot%20on%20the%20map%20to%20now%20being%20a%20hub%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nore