en-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-500x315.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-768x484.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-1536x969.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-2048x1292.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-150x95.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rooms%20at%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Home%20are%20furnished%20in%20a%20way%20that%20modernity%20is%20coupled%20with%20heritage%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20estate%20came%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituated%20right%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20the%20glorious%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20Shreedev%20shares%20that%20the%20main%20draw%20at%20Woodway%20is%20the%20heritage%20and%20history%20associated%20with%20it.%20Built%20in%20the%20classic%20Gothic%20architectural%20style%2C%20one%20feels%20the%20magic%20right%20upon%20entering%20through%20its%20doors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20British%20gentleman%20owned%20the%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreedev.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20he%20had%20initially%20constructed%20a%20bungalow%20on%20the%20highest%20point%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20planned%20on%20living%20in%20it%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20water%20forced%20him%20to%20move%20lower%20down%20on%20the%20land%20and%20build%20a%20smaller%20house.%20Today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324508%2Fbest-pet-friendly-homestays-across-india-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5