%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Less%20Water%2C%20Higher%20Yield%3A%20Why%20PAU%20Prof%E2%80%99s%20Patented%20Hydroponics%20Tech%20Could%20be%20a%20Game%20Changer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20Agricultural%20University%20(PAU)%20was%20recently%20in%20the%20news%20for%20developing%20and%20patenting%20the%20first%20indigenous%20Hybrid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311587%2Fnashik-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-saffron-in-shipping-container-hyroponics-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHydroponic%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HHT)%20developed%20by%20Dr%20V%20P%20Sethi%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20department%20of%20mechanical%20engineering%20of%20the%20college.%20He%20says%20this%20technology%20could%20reduce%20water%20wastage%20by%2090%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Sethi%20explained%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20its%20applicability%20in%20real-time%2C%20and%20why%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20such%20technology%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20changing%20environment%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F135260%2Fladakh-ice-stupa-chorten-buddhism-global-warming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20global%20warming%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20agricultural%20needs%20of%20an%20ever-growing%20population%20will%20be%20hard%20to%20satisfy%20with%20our%20current%20technology.%20Scientists%20and%20agriculturalists%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20have%20been%20researching%20sustainable%20ways%20of%20increasing%20food%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20technology%20like%20HHT%20is%20needed%20for%20many%20reasons.%20I%20have%20travelled%20across%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Japan%20and%20seen%20scientists%20working%20hard%20to%20develop%20technologies%20for%20agri